SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Feature] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, 0),
(@p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 1),
(@p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, 2),
(@p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, 3)) AS i ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [IsActive], [ProjectFeatureId], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [IsActive], [ProjectFeatureId], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId])
VALUES (i.[AddDate], i.[AddUserId], i.[DeleteDate], i.[DeleteUserId], i.[IsActive], i.[ProjectFeatureId], i.[ProjectId], i.[UpdateDate], i.[UpdateUserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[IsDeleted] FROM [Feature] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Feature] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, 0),
(@p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 1),
(@p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, 2),
(@p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, 3)) AS i ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [IsActive], [ProjectFeatureId], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [IsActive], [ProjectFeatureId], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId])
VALUES (i.[AddDate], i.[AddUserId], i.[DeleteDate], i.[DeleteUserId], i.[IsActive], i.[ProjectFeatureId], i.[ProjectId], i.[UpdateDate], i.[UpdateUserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[IsDeleted] FROM [Feature] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Feature] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, 0),
(@p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 1),
(@p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, 2),
(@p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, 3)) AS i ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [IsActive], [ProjectFeatureId], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [IsActive], [ProjectFeatureId], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId])
VALUES (i.[AddDate], i.[AddUserId], i.[DeleteDate], i.[DeleteUserId], i.[IsActive], i.[ProjectFeatureId], i.[ProjectId], i.[UpdateDate], i.[UpdateUserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[IsDeleted] FROM [Feature] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
